snippet.title: The Winter War - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The Winter War releases on January 25th and brings 140+ new cards to Mythgard. Check out some early gameplay here and decide where you stand in the war between the alliance and the rebellion.

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rhinogamesinc.mythgard
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/839910/Mythgard/
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/mythgard/id1404458505
